Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No manners at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to try it, too, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You do, right? I know you wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A week has passed since Shoko's declaration of independence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dorssia and ARUS' militaries are waiting to see who will blink first,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and as a result, Module 77 has found itself in an almost anticiimactic peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're establishing a set of rules, and are getting by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Admittedly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in this Neverland that's free of adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we're enjoying ourselves quite a bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things with Shoko are exactly the way they used to be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Disappointingly enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's use this to load up the supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys make the laws, and you're also the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to try driving one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Otamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,You're paying for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,State of progress is 63%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The evacuation team is slightly behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, what do we do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if they went "Oo!" and then "Vroom vroom vroom!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The retrieval team is ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we assigned some of them to the evacuation team?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Student Council President for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we're farther away from the artificial sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The system is working hard to make sure we don't get too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.09,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep the temperature at 28°C at all times!!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're officially recognizing them, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't give in to their childish threats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(350,350)}ARUS, Office of the President{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, but support for them among ARUS citizens is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking ahead to the next election, it would be a good idea to side with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These are children we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to humor them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your priorities straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The real threat to our country is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(300,400)}Dorssia Military Pact Federation Capital{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the state?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What one thing above all else does every citizen require and desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is - life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There can be no freedom or equality without life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how just the cause or sound the reasoning, without power, they fall on deaf ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The state is power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not forget the tragedy of Red Thursday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We will change the future, and on the blood of our lost comrades,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we will win absolute, undisputed victory for Dorssia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond JIOR... no, far beyond the technological level of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Tokishima... what demon did you make a deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! Professor Kibukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still recuperating, and yet what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, I'm going to stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to figure out what this thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets my physics teacher blood boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! You're the oldest person here, not to mention a proper teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to keep everyone in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not cut out for that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that to you, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I created a page for people to make donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Money again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Money is important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It lets you buy food and medicine, and even hire mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How much have we collected?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You were expecting to make more, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If each one of your friends had donated just 1 yen, we'd have 700 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic! Call an electrician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a malfunction in the environmental regulation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse coils' charged current could be causing a magnetic field resonance with other systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which would throw the central air temperature system out of whack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's trying to set the entire Module into winter mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's interfering with the magnetic field distribution, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about triangular wave interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I love machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, otaku are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All professionals are otaku at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I wasn't volunteering!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Otamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep climbing, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but we're so high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only person who knows this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some backbone! Aren't you a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the boys will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it me, or has it gotten colder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's absolute zero outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you getting sick on us, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Lifeform Gyaora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? This look like the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably... around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the control panel, so it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you are one clumsy nerd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it was down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be nice and warm soon, and your mom is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk irresponsibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get right down to it, you got us into this mess, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's all because you said we should declare independence, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was insane to think we could found a country by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You just went with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:57.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sewing Room.Writing on the desks and food and drink are strictly prohibited."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost all the way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And... got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Miss Rukino didn't mean anything by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She should watch her tone when addressing an upperclassman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does her being a former entertainer make her a bigshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.76,Alt,,0,0,0,,What's going on out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be fighting amongst—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet, Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't address the student council president in such a familiar manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you call him that, too. Call him Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I thought, it's useless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think your gunshot wound might still be—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.81,Alt,,0,0,0,,Just do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.16,Alt,,0,0,0,,Everybody out there is gonna freeze to death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any more of my classmates to die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is against school rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the cause of all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.51,Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What good is fighting going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima, let's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when the whole world is our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you some manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mob rule and violence, interesting "manners" you have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking back to Takahi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so uppity, first-year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're schoolmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Violence doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, call it discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:47.91,Alt,,0,0,0,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2... 3... Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jingle bells, jingle bells jingle all the way... Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again, spouting crazy talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that singing would warm our bodies and our souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think! It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights are on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, that thing you did—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, we're connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're connected to the external net via encrypted channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the mic feed already hooked up to this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're ready over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,People of JIOR, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're all safe. We're doing fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to tell you that, so we all, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We all decided to broadcast this video!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, enjoy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"SAKIMORI ACADEMY"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgetting your cell phone at home,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}fghting with the person you like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some days, nothing seems to go your way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But just eat a tasty dinner{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and hang out with your goofy friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because of stuff like that that we'll be able to give our best again tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs28\frz347.8\pos(765.333,46.667)}YOUTH!!\NNever give in,\Nno matter what.\NYouth now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck for you, for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big kiss for you, for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For our life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just all-out like that all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you are hero in your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I am hero in my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome to our life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go have fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all these viewers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being accessed from ARUS, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's really no such thing as a lost lamb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Fighting spirit", "Sprint flat out", "Sakimori Sports Club"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone has nights that wreck their self-confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haggard faces on the weekend from night after night of no sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.87,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"JIOR Spirit!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're here with me and will take me to the sun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck for you, for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big kiss for you, for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For our life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't keep on smiling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you are hero in your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I am hero in my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this life that's full of thrills, let's go have fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People of JIOR! We're all fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this song reaches you, I know we'll meet again one day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was for that song to reach our families, but it looks like it reached the people of ARUS, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's reached the people of JIOR, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's get Haruto to write a thank-you post!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exploration party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we should know this Module inside and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave that part to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming along as record-keeper, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I meant the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you hated doing that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't done any singing since I got into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more curses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind keeping this a secret just between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want there to be any more people like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But in return, let's be lonely together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(640,668.667)}"Is this sex?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 6,\N"Saki, Come Back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will expose the truth of the world.
